name: ImmutableStack_peekTest
description: Unit tests for the peek functionality of the ImmutableStack class.

test_cases.name: testPeekReturnsTopElement
test_cases.description: Tests that peek returns the top element of the stack.

test_cases.name: testPeekOnEmptyStack
test_cases.description: Tests the behavior of peek on an empty stack.

test_cases.name: testPeekAfterPushAndPop
test_cases.description: Tests peek after pushing and popping elements from the stack.

test_cases.name: testPeekAfterMultiplePushes
test_cases.description: Tests peek after multiple pushes to the stack.

test_cases.name: testPeekAfterMultiplePushesAndPops
test_cases.description: Tests peek after multiple pushes and pops to and from the stack.
